a Pacers]]) <small>(1/1)</small>\n|{{sortname|Tracy|McGrady}} ([[Houston Rockets]]) <small>(1/2)</small>\n|align=center|\n|-\n|align=center|{{Hs|02}}Nov. 5 \u2013 Nov. 11\n|{{sortname|Kevin|Garnett}} ([[Boston Celtics]]) <small>(1/3)</small>\n|{{sortname|Yao|Ming}} ([[Houston Rockets]]) <small>(1/1)</small>\n|align=center|\n|-\n|align=center|{{Hs|03}}Nov. 12 \u2013 Nov. 18\n|{{sortname|Dwight|Howard}} ([[Orlando Magic]]) <small>(1/2)</small>\n|{{sortname|Allen|Iverson}} ([[Denver Nuggets]]) <small>(1/3)</small>\n|align=center|\n|-\n|align=center|{{Hs|04}}Nov. 19 \u2013 Nov. 25\n|{{sortname|LeBron|James}} ([[Cleveland Cavaliers]]) <small>(1/3)</small>\n|{{sortname|Tony|Parker}} ([[San Antonio Spurs]]) <small>(1/1)</small>\n|align=center|\n|-\n|align=center|{{Hs|05}}Nov. 26 \u2013 Dec. 2\n|{{sortname|Dwight|Howard}} ([[Orlando Magic]]) <small>(2/2)</small>\n|{{sortname|Stephen|Jackson}} ([[Golden State Warriors]]) <small>(1/1)</small>\n|align=center|\n|-\n|align=center|{{Hs|06}}Dec. 3 \u2013 Dec. 9\n|{{sortname|Josh|Smith}} ([[Atlanta Hawks]]) <small>(1/1)</small>\n|{{sortname|Brandon|Roy}} ([[Portland Trail Blazers]]) <small>(1/2)</small>\n|align=center|\n|-\n|align=center|{{Hs|07}}Dec. 10 \u2013 Dec. 16\n|{{sortname|Paul|Pierce}} ([[Boston Celtics]]) <small>(1/2)</small>\n|{{sortname|Brandon|Roy}} ([[Portland Trail Blazers]]) <small>(2/2)</small>\n|align=center|\n|-\n|align=center|{{Hs|08}}Dec. 17 \u2013 Dec. 23\n|{{sortname|Joe|Johnson|dab=basketball}} ([[Atlanta Hawks]]) <small>(1/2)</small>\n|{{sortname|Carmelo|Anthony}} ([[Denver Nuggets]]) <small>(1/2)</small>\n|align=center|\n|-\n|align=center|{{Hs|09}}Dec. 24 \u2013 Dec. 30\n|{{sortname|Paul|Pierce}} ([[Boston Celtics]]) <small>(2/2)</small>\n|{{sortname|Chris|Paul}} ([[New Orleans Hornets]]) <small>(1/2)</small>\n|align=center|\n|-\n|align=center|{{Hs|10}}Dec. 31 \u2013 Jan. 6\n|{{sortname|LeBron|James}} ([[Cleveland Cavaliers]]) <small>(2/3)</small>\n|{{sortname|Allen|Iverson}} ([[Denver Nuggets]]) <small>(